name: Mark Gordon
tweet: The world lost a true statesman and devoted public servant. From WWII Veteran to Congressman, UN Ambassador to U.S. President, George H.W. Bush defined for a generation what it means to put country above self. Jennie and I send our thoughts and prayers to the entire Bush family.

name: Mark Gordon
